{
  "stem": "747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or we went down-- we went down the main floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a fence between us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in an odd moments, when there was not Nazis around, we could talk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just here and there, a snatch of conversation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sent us with a little stone, wrapped in a stone to throw over a little message, what we smuggled into his wife.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day we took the wife out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody from us, and stayed home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she came out, and they saw each other for a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then came the uprising.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Unfortunately, Leo was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- no, it was over a big iron gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were on the angle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here was the wall, it was the door, and we were-- we were-- in this corner, it was the tower.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we just thought, what is going on in the yard as they were marching by the fence, inside to the yard?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- after that, I never went-- I mean, if I could help it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was cleaning the other side of-- another corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one day, that was exactly the 7th-- I checked it out, and I studied books-- 7th of October was an uprising in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was started quietly in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We washed the windows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we sat down, and we were talking, praying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very religious, and I was never so religious in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was just full with hope that we will make it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unbelievable, but that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And while we were sitting on the floor, we didn't want to see what's going on, because the wood was about this high, and from there with the windows.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- we didn't wanted to be seen.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
